# 07 - Recipe Creator
# Generate recipes based on ingredients

NAME recipe-creator
INPUT ingredients
INPUT cuisine DEFAULT "any"
INPUT dietary DEFAULT "none"

GOAL brainstorm "Given $ingredients, list 2-3 $cuisine dish ideas respecting $dietary restrictions. One line each."
GOAL select "Pick the simplest recipe that uses most ingredients."
GOAL detail "Write recipe: ingredients list + 5-8 steps max. Save to recipe-output.md."

RUN create USING brainstorm, select, detail
